4. Config 设计
4.1 .projmap/config.toml
[project]name = "auto"root = "."[scan]include_extensions = [".md", ".txt"]include_filenames = ["TODO", "TODO.md", "CLAUDE.md", "README.md"]include_git_log = truegit_log_limit = 200ignore_paths = [  ".git",  ".projmap",  ".venv",  "venv",  "node_modules",  "dist",  "build",  "data",  "__pycache__",  ".pytest_cache"]ignore_globs = [  "*.pyc",  "*.parquet",  "*.csv",  "*.duckdb",  "*.db",  "*.sqlite",  "*.png",  "*.jpg",  "*.jpeg",  "*.gif",  "*.pdf"][chunking]max_chars = 12000overlap_chars = 800[llm]provider = "anthropic"model = "claude-3-5-sonnet-latest"api_key_env = "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY"temperature = 0[dedup]method = "normalized_content_hash"similarity_threshold = 0.88[storage]database_path = ".projmap/projmap.duckdb"cache_dir = ".projmap/cache"

5. Scanner 设计
5.1 扫描对象
默认扫描：
.md.txtTODOTODO.mdREADME.mdCLAUDE.mdhandoff*.md*_handoff.md
额外生成一个 virtual file：
__git_log__
内容来自：
git log --date=iso --pretty=format:"%h | %ad | %s" -n 200
5.2 忽略规则
必须默认忽略：
.git.projmap.venvvenvnode_modulesdistbuilddata__pycache__.pytest_cache
必须默认忽略大文件类型：
.parquet.csv.duckdb.db.sqlite.png.jpg.jpeg.gif.pdf
5.3 FileRecord
scanner 输出统一结构：
class FileRecord(BaseModel):    path: str    file_type: str    content: str    content_hash: str    size_bytes: int    modified_at: datetime | None    status: Literal["new", "changed", "unchanged"]    is_virtual: bool = False

6. Chunker 设计
6.1 Chunk 规则
MVP 不做复杂 token chunk，先用字符数。
max_chars = 12000overlap_chars = 800
切块时尽量在 markdown heading 或空行处分割。
6.2 ChunkRecord
class ChunkRecord(BaseModel):    id: str    file_path: str    chunk_index: int    content: str    content_hash: str    start_line: int | None    end_line: int | None
chunk_id 生成规则：
sha256(file_path + chunk_index + content_hash)

7. LLM Extraction 设计
7.1 默认只支持 Anthropic
MVP 只实现：
provider = anthropicapi_key_env = ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
不要第一版就做复杂 provider abstraction。
可以预留接口：
class BaseExtractor:    def extract(chunk: ChunkRecord) -> ExtractionResult:        ...
但只实现：
AnthropicExtractor

7.2 Extraction Prompt
System Prompt
You are extracting a project decision memory graph.Extract only information that is explicitly supported by the provided document chunk.Return strict JSON only. Do not include markdown. Do not include commentary.Node types:- decision: a concrete project choice, architecture decision, product decision, implementation direction, or accepted plan- risk: a known risk, blocker, weakness, uncertainty, or failure mode- assumption: a belief or condition that the project depends on- version: a named project version, system version, model version, milestone, or frozen baseline- constraint: a rule, limitation, non-negotiable requirement, or "do not modify" boundaryEdge relationship types:- depends-on: source requires target to be true or available- conflicts-with: source contradicts target- supersedes: source replaces target- traces-back-to: source evolved from target- mitigates: source reduces or addresses target riskRules:- Every node must include evidence_quote from the chunk.- Every edge must include evidence_quote from the chunk.- Do not invent facts.- Do not infer relationships without textual evidence.- Do not generate IDs.- If no valid nodes or edges exist, return empty arrays.- Keep node content concise: one sentence.- Keep detail under 500 characters.
User Prompt
Extract project memory nodes and edges from this document chunk.Source file:{source_file}Chunk index:{chunk_index}Content:{chunk_content}Return JSON in this exact shape:{  "nodes": [    {      "type": "decision | risk | assumption | version | constraint",      "content": "one sentence summary",      "detail": "supporting detail under 500 chars",      "source_line": "heading or approximate line if available",      "evidence_quote": "short direct quote from chunk",      "confidence": 0.0    }  ],  "edges": [    {      "from_content": "must match or closely match a node content",      "to_content": "must match or closely match a node content",      "relationship": "depends-on | conflicts-with | supersedes | traces-back-to | mitigates",      "evidence_quote": "short direct quote from chunk",      "confidence": 0.0    }  ]}

8. Schema 设计
8.1 Node schema
from typing import Literalfrom pydantic import BaseModel, FieldNodeType = Literal[    "decision",    "risk",    "assumption",    "version",    "constraint",]class ExtractedNode(BaseModel):    type: NodeType    content: str = Field(min_length=5, max_length=300)    detail: str = Field(default="", max_length=500)    source_line: str | None = None    evidence_quote: str = Field(min_length=5, max_length=1000)    confidence: float = Field(ge=0.0, le=1.0)
8.2 Edge schema
EdgeType = Literal[    "depends-on",    "conflicts-with",    "supersedes",    "traces-back-to",    "mitigates",]class ExtractedEdge(BaseModel):    from_content: str = Field(min_length=5, max_length=300)    to_content: str = Field(min_length=5, max_length=300)    relationship: EdgeType    evidence_quote: str = Field(min_length=5, max_length=1000)    confidence: float = Field(ge=0.0, le=1.0)
8.3 Extraction result
class ExtractionResult(BaseModel):    nodes: list[ExtractedNode] = []    edges: list[ExtractedEdge] = []

9. DuckDB 表结构
9.1 files
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS files (  path TEXT PRIMARY KEY,  file_type TEXT,  content_hash TEXT,  size_bytes BIGINT,  modified_at TIMESTAMP,  last_scanned_at TIMESTAMP,  last_extracted_at TIMESTAMP,  status TEXT);
9.2 chunks
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS chunks (  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,  file_path TEXT,  chunk_index INTEGER,  content TEXT,  content_hash TEXT,  start_line INTEGER,  end_line INTEGER,  created_at TIMESTAMP);
9.3 nodes
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS nodes (  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,  type TEXT,  content TEXT,  detail TEXT,  source_file TEXT,  source_chunk_id TEXT,  source_line TEXT,  evidence_quote TEXT,  confidence DOUBLE,  content_hash TEXT,  created_at TIMESTAMP,  updated_at TIMESTAMP);
9.4 edges
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS edges (  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,  from_node_id TEXT,  to_node_id TEXT,  relationship TEXT,  evidence_quote TEXT,  confidence DOUBLE,  source_file TEXT,  source_chunk_id TEXT,  created_at TIMESTAMP);
9.5 extractions
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS extractions (  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,  chunk_id TEXT,  file_path TEXT,  model TEXT,  raw_response TEXT,  parsed_json TEXT,  status TEXT,  error TEXT,  created_at TIMESTAMP);

10. ID 生成规则
10.1 File hash
sha256(file_content)
10.2 Chunk ID
sha256(file_path + chunk_index + chunk_content_hash)
10.3 Node ID
MVP 使用 deterministic ID，方便重复 rebuild 不产生大量重复节点。
sha256(node_type + normalized_content)
10.4 Edge ID
sha256(from_node_id + to_node_id + relationship)

11. Dedup 设计
11.1 MVP 方案
先不用 embedding dedup。
使用 deterministic dedup：
same node_type+ normalized_content_hash 相同= same node
11.2 normalized_content
规则：
1. lower()2. strip()3. 合并多个空格4. 去掉末尾标点
11.3 可选 fuzzy dedup
可用 Python 标准库：
difflib.SequenceMatcher
规则：
same node_typeAND similarity > 0.88
但建议先关闭 fuzzy dedup，避免误合并。

12. Incremental Rebuild 设计
12.1 文件级增量
每次 rebuild：
1. scanner 计算当前 content_hash2. 读取 files 表中的旧 content_hash3. 如果 hash 一样 → skip4. 如果 hash 不一样 → re-chunk + re-extract
12.2 变化文件处理
对于 changed file：
1. 删除该文件旧 chunks2. 删除该文件旧 extractions3. 删除该文件旧 nodes / edges4. 重新插入新结果
MVP 可以先按 source_file 级别重建，简单可靠。
12.3 unchanged file
必须跳过：
LLM extractionchunk rebuildnode insertedge insert

13. Edge Resolution 设计
LLM 返回的 edge 使用：
from_contentto_content
系统负责解析到 node_id。
13.1 解析规则
1. 先在当前 chunk nodes 中找 exact normalized match2. 找不到则在当前 file nodes 中找 exact normalized match3. 仍找不到则丢弃该 edge，并记录 warning
13.2 为什么不让 LLM 生成 ID
因为 LLM 生成 ID 不稳定，重复 rebuild 会产生不可控结果。

14. Error Handling
14.1 没有 API Key
场景：
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY missing
行为：
projmap rebuild exits with clear message不写入部分 extractionexit code = 1
输出：
Missing ANTHROPIC_API_KEY.Set it with:export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="your-key"
14.2 单个 chunk 抽取失败
行为：
1. 写入 extractions 表2. status = failed3. error = exception message4. 继续处理下一个 chunk
14.3 JSON parse 失败
行为：
1. raw_response 写入 extractions2. status = json_parse_failed3. error 写入 parse error4. 继续处理
14.4 Pydantic validation 失败
行为：
1. raw_response 写入 extractions2. status = validation_failed3. error 写入 validation error4. 继续处理
14.5 非 Git repo
projmap init 不应该失败。
行为：
1. 正常初始化2. include_git_log 自动设为 false3. 输出 warning

